Package: pidgin-conversation-locker
Version: 1.2-0
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: pidgin (>= 1.2.5.0)
Maintainer: Peeyoosh Sangolekar <peeyoosh.sangolekar@gmail.com>
Homepage: http://pidgin-conversation-locker.googlecode.com
Description: A pidgin plugin that prevents closing of important conversations
 Prevents closing of important conversations by locking(restricting close) them.
 Lock/unlock button is added on each conversation with which conversation can be
 locked/unlocked.
 .
 Also prompts user if he tries to close window containing locked conversations
 if any.

